---
title: Vietnamese-Style Pork & Slaw Bowl with Crispy Shallots & Fried Egg
description: Discover classic Vietnamese flavours with a low-carb twist! Take crunchy slaw piled with saucy pork mince and a fried egg, and
you’ve got a dinner-time hit. Serve with quick-pickled onion for an extra punch of flavour.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
